{"tid":2408411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊：《党安法》檢控數字偏低","createTime":"2021-02-15T02:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T02:36:04.000Z","uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4afd38c8dcaaa354cbf8543eef77f60ff69fd62","tid":2408411,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:34:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379057/%E5%8F%B8%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%85%E6%84%8F%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379057%2F%25E5%258F%25B8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%2585%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=d7609795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379057/%E5%8F%B8%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%85%E6%84%8F%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n律政司長鄭若驊接受本台訪問時，回應有評論指，《港區國安法》實施以來，檢控人數偏低。她解釋，由於檢控門檻高於拘捕門檻，要證明有合理定罪機會，在部分案件，律政司等待警方作進一步蒐證。對於終審法院近日審議一宗《國安法》相關的保釋上訴，沒有海外非常任法官參與，鄭若驊認為有關爭議「有少許借題發揮」，說判斷裁決公正與否，最重要是看法官判詞。 鄭若驊說《國安法》實施以來，香港社會平穩下來、由亂及治，但有些人故意，或者由於不清晰，而對《國安法》錯誤理解。她說本港法治基礎仍然穩固，作為仲裁及國際法律中心地位不變。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379057&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=a8577dd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379057</a>"},{"pid":"b9773abbb193f955ac0f767e1ddee2ee89fb51ea","tid":2408411,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"咁即係鳩拉？"}]}